<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="219" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,834,1903]" pageId="18" pageNumber="219">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,942,967]" pageId="18" pageNumber="219">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific name is a patronym in honor of the collector F. Ballarin; noun (name) in genitive case.
</paragraph>
